data.title: National Register Sites in Orangeburg County
data.text:
The National Register of Historic Places:

National Register Sites in Orangeburg County, SC

The following properties in Orangeburg County have been listed in the National Register as historic sites or districts. From each site is a link to the original nomination in Adobe PDF format.

Note: most National Register properties are privately owned and are not open to the public. The privacy of owners should be respected. Not all properties retain the same integrity as when originally documented and listed in the National Register due to changes and modifications over time.
